Package: libpixelif-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Provides localization data for libpixelif.
 This package is required by all packages which are utilizing libpixelif.

Package: libpixelif-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libpixelif-common,
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: This interface translates raw Z-Machine output to pixels.
 This library transforms fizmo's raw Z-Machine output into pixel draw commands.

